title: Cleveland police arrest protester at City Hall during demonstration calling for 'justice for Tamir' (video)
text:
Cleveland police arrest protester at City Hall during demonstration calling for 'justice for Tamir' (video) 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
CLEVELAND, Ohio -- Cleveland police arrested a protester -- calling for justice for Tamir Rice -- during Monday night's City Council meeting...
